00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:08.840
[Amit Varma]: making her mark in the literary world and in media.

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:13.200
[Amit Varma]: There were so many subjects I wanted to talk to her about, our society, our languages,

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:17.480
